First we start with running the below command which starts POX server.

sudo python ~/pox/pox.py forwarding.l2_multi openflow.discovery --eat-early-packets openflow.spanning_tree --no-flood --hold-down

Then in the other terminal we run the python code.
Which asks for no. of switches and no. of hosts.And all get created.
